text: Sahi hai bhai Techkriti'21 mei itne competitions ke problem statement bannaye hai and logo ke random questions ke answer kiye hai ki abb har question jana pahchana sa lgta hai...Tumhara sath kamm kr ke mazza aya hamara december 1st week ke badd ka schedule yadd hai after 12noon daily baith kr kamm krna..koi workshop schedule hona and then workshop company nhi milna kya din the...and then final 3 days of Techkriti'21 (12-14 March)....and yarr hamara beech mei kamm to kabhi distribute hua hi nhi bas mission same tha ki Techkriti'21 karani hai and karayi bhi...I hope future mei bhi sath mei aise hi mile and sath mei kamm kre
author: Ankur  Bajaj

text:
Hello Beta,
kaise hoo, yadd nhi krte hoo bhool gaye kya Bacche ho tum dil pr na lio mazze kr rha hu joo hamm mostly krte hi the. Yarr tumne hi mere passwords le lekar sikhaya hai log kaise cheat krte hai different platform ka use krke..apna sath mei  mei CC jana and vha bhi beech beech mei aa kr backchodi katna and tera fraud marne ki style to god level hai ..jab bhi GPL ke liye sab ayye to roo dena and jis din BBQ se aakr GPL hui thi usme maine bhi damm se pela tha but jis chapal  pr discussion hua tha badd mei  voo meri nhi thi..kabb aa rha hai samman lene IITK batta dio fir sath hi mumbai chalenge.
author: Ankur  Bajaj

text: Hello Monu, Kya mei bolu hamm to vo hai joo samne hoo to bina bole hi jann jate the ki kya bolne wala hai..but tere sath room mate banna tumse bahut kuch seekha..mere social media pr accounts create krna and jab mei password change kr du then tera unke password gauss krna and tumhare sath mei ground jana, JOSH'19 mei athletics mei as a team participate krna, college fest mei kamm krna, questions discuss krna and ekk barr kuch bhi bol du usko mann lena..yarr aise hi rhna. Abhi to city alag alag hai jha pr hamme jana hai..pr ye doori bhi door na kr payengi  ye vadda rha..milte rhenge and jaise the vaise hi rhenge.
author: Ankur  Bajaj

text:
Hello DOPA! 
Yadd hai mujhe voo ratt jis din tumhe ye title mila tha...meri sabse phle IITK mei tumse hi banani start hui thi apna sath mei freshers night ki dance practice mei jana, atheletics mei sath jana but tera late anna, GPL tabb takk lena jab takk chapal na toot jaye, meri cover cover letter, resume mei help krna, sab badiya tha yarr but kitni jaldi ye apna time nikle gya samjh hi nhi aya. Joo line sabse jayada soot krti hai tum pr "IITK ka backchod launda"..kuch bhi le loo Academic, sports, bakati..sabme ekk number.. sabke sath mazze mei rhna tumhare pass to unknown logo ke sath bhi discuss krne ko kuch na kuch hota hi tha..ye mujhe bhi sikha doo kaise krte hoo socha tha final year mei seekh lunga. Aise hi rhna.. Aoo kanpur milte hai jaldi se..
author: Ankur  Bajaj
